These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Birthday: june, january, september, november
1. Birthday:january is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:november is between Birthday:june and Birthday:january##2
3. Birthday:november is on the right of Birthday:june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | june | november | january | september |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: scientific, zombie, crime, spy
1. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left of Movie-Genre:spy##1
2. Movie-Genre:zombie is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:scientific##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific | spy | crime |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Sport: surfing, lacrosse, tennis, cycling
1. Sport:cycling is on the left or right of Sport:surfing##3
2. Sport:surfing is in an odd position##4
3. Sport:tennis is between Sport:cycling and Sport:lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Sport   | surfing | cycling | tennis | lacrosse |

