1. Music-Genre:trance is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:dubstep is on the far left or far right##3
3. Music-Genre:trance is between Music-Genre:dubstep and Music-Genre:salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | salsa | trance | dubstep |

