.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Cigar: havana, siglo, fonseca, bluemaster
1. Cigar:siglo == Cigar:siglo##1
2. Cigar:bluemaster is on the left or right of Cigar:fonseca##3
3. Cigar:fonseca is on the far left or far right##3
4. Cigar:havana is in an even position##4
5. Cigar:bluemaster is on the left of Cigar:siglo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | fonseca | bluemaster | siglo | havana |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
Birthday: august, october, september, march
1. Birthday:september is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:march is on the left of Birthday:september##1
3. Birthday:september is on the left or right of Birthday:october##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | august | march | september | october |

 